sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant UI as Project Settings / Team
    participant API as Project API (/api/projects)
    participant DB as Supabase DB
    participant Email as Email Service (IndiePitcher)

    Admin->>UI: Add Member to Project
    UI->>UI: Validate Email Format
    UI->>API: POST /api/projects/:id/members {userId, role: "Member"}
    
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
    API->>DB: INSERT into project_members
    DB-->>API: 201 Created
    API->>Email: sendProjectMemberAdded({to: email, projectName: "..."})
    Email->>Email: Resolve Template: "project-member-added"
    Email-->>Admin: Email Sent Confirmation
    end
    
    API-->>UI: 200 OK (Member Object)
    UI->>UI: Update Local Team State (Member List)
    
    Admin->>UI: Update Project Details
    UI->>API: PATCH /api/projects/:id {name, key, owner_id}
    API->>API: Generate unique key from name if missing
    API->>DB: UPDATE projects SET ...
    DB-->>API: Success
    API-->>UI: 200 OK
    
    UI->>API: GET /api/projects/:id/stats
    API->>DB: COUNT(*) FROM tasks WHERE project_id = :id GROUP BY status
    DB-->>API: { "To Do": 10, "Done": 5, ... }
    API-->>UI: { total: 15, completed: 5, percentage: 33.3 }
    UI->>UI: Re-render Progress Radial Chart
